        {
          "speaker": "B",
          "chinese": "我是坐飞机来的。飞机票很贵。",
          "pinyin": "Wǒ shì zuò fēijī lái de. Fēijī piào hěn guì.",
          "english": "I came by airplane. The plane ticket is very expensive."
